It’s changed me, in part by helping me find deep and quiet spaces to evaluate what I’m doing with my life.
So before I get any further into this story, the news: I’m shutting down NMPolitics.net.
I’m moving on to things other than political journalism, at least for now.
Klein believes we have built a political system in which it is, at the very least, difficult for people to express the best versions of themselves.
I’m sharing much of my photography and writing on Facebook and Instagram @haussamen and will share news about future endeavors.